國　　110 　年　　10　　月　　18　　日\r\n                              書記官  劉淑慧","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDV/110%2c%e6%b3%95%2c76%2c20211018%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDV,110,法,76,20211018,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"法","JNO":"76","JDATE":"20211018","JTITLE":"變更捐助章程"}